Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢 我做不了夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從光芒籠罩了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從大地隆起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從一君消失的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從8個月前的那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就夢不到那個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}害怕受到傷害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}很享受順利而狡猾的生活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}終點明擺著的旅途 有什麼好拽的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}比起被灌輸的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}更願選擇一時的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}預定調和？ 乏味的想打哈欠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}「誰都不會理解」如此苦惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}如果用冷漠的視線望向這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}無法饒恕 Reflextion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Reckless fire 不負責任的尊嚴都化成灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不會有奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}接近的是偽善者的甜蜜陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}應該相信的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}緊握珍貴的信念不動搖
